 } } \right|$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2}[6(7 - 3) - 2(4 + 2) + 1(12 + 14)]$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2}(24 - 12 + 26) = {1 \over 2}(12 + 26)$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2} \times 38$$<br><br>= 19 sq units

